COMMITTEE AMENDMENT
(Date)
I move to amend Senate Bill No. 1365, on Page 4, Line 18, by deleting SECTION 3 in its entirety,
inserting a new SECTION 3 to read as follows, and amending the title to conform:
“SECTION 3. It being immediately necessary for the preservation of the public peace, health
or safety, an emergency is hereby declared to exist, by reason whereof this act shall take effect and
be in full force from and after its passage and approval.”
